From: Steffen Jaeckel <sjaeckel@suse.de>
Subject: kABI fix for mptcp: add sk_stop_timer_sync helper
Patch-mainline: Never, kABI workaround
References: CVE-2024-35910 bsc#1224489

Upstream commit 08b81d873126 ("mptcp: add sk_stop_timer_sync
helper") introduced a new API to include/net/sock.h, hide it for the
kABI checker.

Signed-off-by: Steffen Jaeckel <sjaeckel@suse.de>

---
 include/net/sock.h | 2 ++
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+)

diff --git a/include/net/sock.h b/include/net/sock.h
index fe03879f04da7..899e56b8e25fd 100644
--- a/include/net/sock.h
+++ b/include/net/sock.h
@@ -2130,7 +2130,9 @@ void sk_reset_timer(struct sock *sk, struct timer_list *timer,
 
 void sk_stop_timer(struct sock *sk, struct timer_list *timer);
 
+#ifndef __GENKSYMS__
 void sk_stop_timer_sync(struct sock *sk, struct timer_list *timer);
+#endif
 
 int __sk_queue_drop_skb(struct sock *sk, struct sk_buff_head *sk_queue,
 			struct sk_buff *skb, unsigned int flags,
-- 
2.47.1

